and now it's time to store your good work so

5
00:00:08,910 --> 00:00:11,415
that you can hand it over to other stakeholders.

6
00:00:11,415 --> 00:00:13,560
Let's look into how to do this.

7
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:18,990
There are some simple ways of updating a local datastore with clean data for example,

8
00:00:18,990 --> 00:00:22,605
saving data using the Pandas.csv function.

9
00:00:22,605 --> 00:00:25,650
Here we see how we can directly

10
00:00:25,650 --> 00:00:29,685
specify the path and the filename as an input to the.csv function.

11
00:00:29,685 --> 00:00:33,570
It's also sometimes typical to specify index equals false to

12
