32
00:01:35,510 --> 00:01:38,360
You may have a location for storing your documentation of

33
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:40,430
the design decisions and strategies that you

34
00:01:40,430 --> 00:01:42,755
take along the way to assess and clean your data,

35
00:01:42,755 --> 00:01:44,590
as well as your raw data

36
00:01:44,590 --> 00:01:49,145
your source code including your Jupyter Notebooks and the cleaned data files.

37
00:01:49,145 --> 00:01:52,160
This all will make it easier when you decide to create

38
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:56,720
